# Task #124: a pre-existing pairing-expired flag (set earlier by a hook or menu action) puts
# the banner in the menu; the first SUCCESSFUL network engine call clears the flag — honest
# state, no stale banner. Flow: pick the banner (proves it renders), back out of the wizard,
# run a successful Sync now, exit — flag must be gone.
desc menu (#124): pairing-expired banner shows from the flag; a successful sync clears it
config paired
seeded
sdfile Tools/tg5040/Lodor.pak/.pairing-expired
pick 0|! Pairing expired - re-pair
pick 2|
pick 0|Sync now
engine 0|RESULT ok
pick 2|
expect_exit 0
expect_trace LIST[RomM server protocol]
expect_trace PRES timeout=2 msg='Sync complete'
expect_file_absent Tools/tg5040/Lodor.pak/.pairing-expired
